```plantuml
@startuml YW-Ma_Algorithms-Visualizer

actor User
participant "MainInterface.js" as MainInterface
participant "Sidebar.js" as Sidebar
participant "GraphSVG.js" as GraphSVG
participant "GraphTable.js" as GraphTable
participant "Map.js" as Map
participant "eventProxy.js" as EventProxy
participant "routes/index.js" as Backend
participant "modules/Authorize.js" as Authorize
participant "backEnd/bin/exe/DFS" as DFS
participant "external C++ executables" as Executables

User -> MainInterface: Open Application
MainInterface -> Sidebar: Render Sidebar
MainInterface -> Map: Render Map
MainInterface -> GraphSVG: Initialize Graph Visualization
MainInterface -> GraphTable: Initialize Graph Table

User -> Sidebar: Select Algorithm (e.g., DFS)
Sidebar -> MainInterface: Notify Algorithm Selection
MainInterface -> EventProxy: Publish Algorithm Selection Event

EventProxy -> GraphSVG: Subscribe to Algorithm Selection Event
GraphSVG -> Backend: Request Algorithm Execution
Backend -> Authorize: Check User Authorization
Authorize -> Backend: Authorization Result

Backend -> DFS: Execute Algorithm (DFS)
DFS -> Backend: Return Execution Result
Backend -> GraphSVG: Send Execution Steps

GraphSVG -> EventProxy: Publish Animation Steps
EventProxy -> GraphTable: Update Table with Steps
EventProxy -> Map: Update Map with Node Changes

User -> Sidebar: Trigger Visualization
Sidebar -> EventProxy: Notify Visualization Trigger
EventProxy -> GraphSVG: Start Animation
GraphSVG -> User: Display Animation

@enduml
```